interpretation: The "open file folder" card represents organization and structure. It suggests that it is time to sort through your thoughts and ideas in a methodical way. This could be a good time to focus on completing projects or getting things done that you have been putting off. The card also suggests that there may be important documents or information that needs to be reviewed and organized. Take time to assess your priorities and create a plan for achieving your goals. This card can also indicate a need for clarity and transparency in communication. It may be time to open up and share your thoughts and feelings with others. Overall, the "open file folder" card encourages you to take control of your life and get organized.
